<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Defs>
	<AlienRace.ThingDef_AlienRace ParentName="BasePawn">
		<defName>AP_Symbiote</defName>
		<label>Symbiote</label>
		<description>A symbiotic relation between a symbiote and its host. The symbiote is the small creature that stays on top of its host's head. The blood they need are obtained from their host, while they enhance and upgrade their host's senses and abilities in exchange. Their civilizations grew as any others with no noticeable distinctions. They developed countries, fought wars and eventually led to a globalized culture. They also developed technology which could do some of the things that hosts previously did, but they still used hosts out of tradition and efficiency. A single symbiote often had different hosts for different tasks.\n\nFemale Symbiotes can lay down larva eggs. A surgery can be performed in any Human pawn to turn them into another Symbiote. Only other Symbiotes can perform this operation.</description>
